data.description: Imagine coming home to this picture-perfect abode nestled in the heart of the Preserve at Haynes Creek, a sought-after sidewalk community that seamlessly blends convenience and charm. This stunning 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle.  Starting with the exterior, the home boasts a timeless brick front complemented by durable concrete siding. The brand-new roof and gutters, equipped with efficient guards, promise years of worry-free living. The wraparound porch, perfect for your morning coffee or an evening read, adds a touch of southern charm, overlooking the lush, colorful landscaping that adorns the property.  Step inside to discover a world of elegance and comfort. A beautiful 2-story foyer with bright hardwood floors welcome you, leading into a formal living room that sets the tone for the home's charming interior. The formal dining room is enriched with chair rail molding, perfect for hosting memorable dinners.  The heart of the home, a large kitchen, features a breakfast area, stainless steel appliances, exquisite countertops, ceramic tile backsplash, ample cabinetry, and a pantry. An office nook provides the perfect space for productivity or quiet reflection.  The family room invites warmth and relaxation with its cozy fireplace, and a rear stairwell leads to the second level. Here, the spacious master bedroom suite awaits. Complete with a tray ceiling, walk-in closet, dual vanity, and a separate garden tub and shower, this is truly a private sanctuary. The remaining bedrooms are generously proportioned, offering ample space for family or guests.  But this home offers more than just a stunning residence. It's located mere steps away from a host of community amenities. Enjoy exclusive access to a pool, tennis courts, clubhouse, and a residents-only park. With robust security measures, you can enjoy this picturesque community with peace of mind. Plus, the convenience of nearby shopping and restaurants enhances the appeal of this location.  Living here means being part of a vibrant, secure community, coming home to a place that's more than just a house, but a space that nurtures and grows with you. So why wait? Come and discover your dream home in the Preserve at Haynes Creek. Your future awaits.
